[2026-03-11 11:08:01] [MODIFICACIÓN] deploy-digitalocean.yml — AGREGADO job e2e-tests (Stage 5) con Playwright against staging. Corre DESPUÉS de smoke-test y ANTES de image-smoke-test. Fallo activa rollback.
