--- HALLAZGOS Y CORRECCIONES ---
1. [CRÍTICO-CORREGIDO] deploy-staging tenía continue-on-error:true — deploy fallido no bloqueaba pipeline
2. [CRÍTICO-CORREGIDO] Integration tests completamente ausentes — test.yml deshabilitado (if:false). Creado nuevo stage en smart-cicd.yml
3. [CRÍTICO-CORREGIDO] E2E tests ausentes del pipeline activo — solo smoke tests post-deploy. Creado stage e2e-tests en deploy-digitalocean.yml
4. [MEDIO-CORREGIDO] Backend format check era non-blocking (continue-on-error:true) — ahora bloquea el build
5. [ALTO-PENDIENTE] Force push protection no implementada en código — requiere config en GitHub repo settings (Branch Protection Rules)
6. [MEDIO-PENDIENTE] Production deploy no requiere aprobación manual — requiere GitHub Environment Protection Rules en settings
7. [BAJO-OK] NuGet vuln audit continue-on-error aceptable — siguiente step hace check explícito de Critical vulns
8. [BAJO-OK] Trivy/SARIF upload continue-on-error aceptable — no es gate de calidad, es upload informativo
9. [BAJO-OK] Slack notification continue-on-error aceptable — fallo de notificación no debe bloquear pipeline

--- PIPELINE RESULTANTE (6 STAGES) ---
Stage 1: Lint + Static Analysis — _reusable-dotnet-service.yml (format check BLOQUEANTE) + _reusable-frontend.yml (lint + typecheck)
Stage 2: Unit Tests — _reusable-dotnet-service.yml (dotnet test --filter exclude Integration/E2E) + _reusable-frontend.yml (vitest --run)
Stage 3: Integration Tests — smart-cicd.yml integration-tests job (Docker Compose + postgres/redis/rabbitmq) [NUEVO]
Stage 4: Docker Build — _reusable-dotnet-service.yml docker job + _reusable-frontend.yml docker job
Stage 5: E2E Tests (Staging) — deploy-digitalocean.yml e2e-tests job (Playwright against staging) [NUEVO]
Stage 6: Deploy + Smoke Tests — deploy-digitalocean.yml (deploy + health-check + smoke-test + image-smoke-test + auto-rollback)

